FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[AccessFailedCount], [u].[AccountType], [u].[AdminApproved], [u].[Avatar], [u].[BoardId], [u].[ConcurrencyStamp], [u].[Email], [u].[EmailConfirmed], [u].[FaceDataId], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LockoutEnabled], [u].[LockoutEnd], [u].[NormalizedEmail], [u].[NormalizedUserName], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [u].[SecurityStamp], [u].[StandardId], [u].[SubjectId], [u].[TwoFactorEnabled], [u].[UserName], [u].[isEnabled]

    WHERE [u].[Id] = @__user_Id_0
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[UserId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AccessFailedCount], [t].[AccountType], [t].[AdminApproved], [t].[Avatar], [t].[BoardId], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[Email], [t].[EmailConfirmed], [t].[FaceDataId], [t].[FirstName], [t].[LastName], [t].[LockoutEnabled], [t].[LockoutEnd], [t].[NormalizedEmail], [t].[NormalizedUserName], [t].[PasswordHash], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t].[SecurityStamp], [t].[StandardId], [t].[SubjectId], [t].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t].[UserName], [t].[isEnabled], [t0].[ClassId], [t0].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[BoardId], [t0].[IsRegistrationAllowed], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StandardId], [t0].[SubjectId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[AccessFailedCount], [u].[AccountType], [u].[AdminApproved], [u].[Avatar], [u].[BoardId], [u].[ConcurrencyStamp], [u].[Email], [u].[EmailConfirmed], [u].[FaceDataId], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LockoutEnabled], [u].[LockoutEnd], [u].[NormalizedEmail], [u].[NormalizedUserName], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [u].[SecurityStamp], [u].[StandardId], [u].[SubjectId], [u].[TwoFactorEnabled], [u].[UserName], [u].[isEnabled]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[Id] = @__user_Id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [u0].[ClassId], [u0].[UserId], [c].[Id], [c].[BoardId], [c].[IsRegistrationAllowed], [c].[Name], [c].[StandardId], [c].[SubjectId]
    FROM [UserClass] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [Classes] AS [c] ON [u0].[ClassId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ClassId], [t0].[UserId]

FROM [Users] AS [u]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[BoardId], [c].[IsRegistrationAllowed], [c].[Name], [c].[StandardId], [c].[SubjectId], [u0].[UserId]
    FROM [UserClass] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [Classes] AS [c] ON [u0].[ClassId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [u].[Id] = [t].[UserId]

SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[AccessFailedCount], [u].[AccountType], [u].[AdminApproved], [u].[Avatar], [u].[BoardId], [u].[ConcurrencyStamp], [u].[Email], [u].[EmailConfirmed], [u].[FaceDataId], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LockoutEnabled], [u].[LockoutEnd], [u].[NormalizedEmail], [u].[NormalizedUserName], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [u].[SecurityStamp], [u].[StandardId], [u].[SubjectId], [u].[TwoFactorEnabled], [u].[UserName], [u].[isEnabled], [t].[ClassId], [t].[UserId], [t].[Id], [t].[BoardId], [t].[IsRegistrationAllowed], [t].[Name], [t].[StandardId], [t].[SubjectId]
FROM [Users] AS [u]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [u0].[ClassId], [u0].[UserId], [c].[Id], [c].[BoardId], [c].[IsRegistrationAllowed], [c].[Name], [c].[StandardId], [c].[SubjectId]
    FROM [UserClass] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [Classes] AS [c] ON [u0].[ClassId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [u].[Id] = [t].[UserId]
WHERE ((([u].[AccountType] = N'Faculty') AND ([u].[BoardId] = @__Parse_0)) AND ([u].[StandardId] = @__FindFirst_Value_1)) AND ([u].[AdminApproved] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [u].[Id], [t].[ClassId], [t].[UserId]

FROM [Users] AS [u]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[BoardId], [c].[IsRegistrationAllowed], [c].[Name], [c].[StandardId], [c].[SubjectId], [u0].[UserId]
    FROM [UserClass] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [Classes] AS [c] ON [u0].[ClassId] = [c].[Id]
